      },
      "date": "2014-07-23 18:15:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: Code-Review+2\n\nOut of curiosity, what triggered your fixing of this code? Was it showing up on profiles, or just something you noticed during code reading?  If there is a significant performance change it is worthwhile to document this in the commit message.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "a3a4364624d49a6c5a8b6aebe40d9995724acb0b",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 419,
        "name": "Frank Zago",
        "email": "fzago@cray.com",
        "username": "fzago.cray"
      },
      "date": "2014-07-23 18:26:27.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\nI'm looking at what our copytool is doing. I believe fid2path is an expensive operation overall, so I looked at it to see if it could be sped up a little. Although that patch doesn't appear to make a difference, it's nevertheless a minor improvement.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 6
    },
